{"id": "art-453", "label": "Art. 453", "title": "Art. 453: Cazurile de revizuire", "slug": "art-453", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1014773175\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1516\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1014773175\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 453:\nCazurile de revizuire </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1836497270\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1515\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1836497270\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Revizuirea\nhot&#259;rârilor judec&#259;tore&#351;ti definitive, cu privire la latura\npenal&#259;, poate fi cerut&#259; când:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1783948137\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1514\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1783948137\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)s-au descoperit fapte sau împrejur&#259;ri ce nu au fost\ncunoscute la solu&#355;ionarea cauzei &#351;i care dovedesc netemeinicia\nhot&#259;rârii pronun&#355;ate în cauz&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_596982529\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1513\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_596982529\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)hot&#259;rârea a c&#259;rei revizuire se cere s-a\nîntemeiat pe declara&#355;ia unui martor, opinia unui expert sau pe\nsitua&#355;iile învederate de un interpret, care a s&#259;vâr&#351;it\ninfrac&#355;iunea de m&#259;rturie mincinoas&#259; în cauza a c&#259;rei\nrevizuire se cere, influen&#355;ând astfel solu&#355;ia pronun&#355;at&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1310332905\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1512\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1310332905\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)un înscris care a servit ca temei al hot&#259;rârii a\nc&#259;rei revizuire se cere a fost declarat fals în cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii\nsau dup&#259; pronun&#355;area hot&#259;rârii, împrejurare care a\ninfluen&#355;at solu&#355;ia pronun&#355;at&#259; în cauz&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1590602769\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1511\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1590602769\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)un membru al completului de judecat&#259;, procurorul ori\npersoana care a efectuat acte de urm&#259;rire penal&#259; a comis o\ninfrac&#355;iune în leg&#259;tur&#259; cu cauza a c&#259;rei revizuire se cere,\nîmprejurare care a influen&#355;at solu&#355;ia pronun&#355;at&#259; în\ncauz&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_258767014\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1510\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_258767014\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)când dou&#259; sau mai multe hot&#259;râri\njudec&#259;tore&#351;ti definitive nu se pot concilia;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_263246493\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1509\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_263246493\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)hot&#259;rârea s-a întemeiat pe o prevedere legal&#259;\ncare, dup&#259; ce hot&#259;rârea a devenit definitiv&#259;, a fost\ndeclarat&#259; neconstitu&#355;ional&#259; ca urmare a admiterii unei\nexcep&#355;ii de neconstitu&#355;ionalitate ridicate în acea cauz&#259;, în\nsitua&#355;ia în care consecin&#355;ele înc&#259;lc&#259;rii dispozi&#355;iei\nconstitu&#355;ionale continu&#259; s&#259; se produc&#259; &#351;i nu pot fi\nremediate decât prin revizuirea hot&#259;rârii pronun&#355;ate.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1666259609\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1508\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1666259609\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Revizuirea hot&#259;rârilor judec&#259;tore&#351;ti\npenale definitive, exclusiv cu privire la latura civil&#259;, poate fi\ncerut&#259; numai în fa&#355;a instan&#355;ei civile, potrivit Codului de\nprocedur&#259; civil&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_806735485\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1507\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_806735485\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cazul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) lit. f) poate fi\ninvocat ca motiv de revizuire numai în favoarea persoanei condamnate sau a\ncelei fa&#355;&#259; de care s-a dispus renun&#355;area la aplicarea pedepsei\nori amânarea aplic&#259;rii pedepsei.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1261556060\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1506\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1261556060\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Cazul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) lit. a) constituie\nmotiv de revizuire dac&#259; pe baza faptelor sau împrejur&#259;rilor noi se\npoate dovedi netemeinicia hot&#259;rârii de achitare, condamnare, de\nrenun&#355;are la aplicarea pedepsei, de amânare a aplic&#259;rii pedepsei ori\nde încetare a procesului penal, iar cazurile prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) lit.\nb)-d) &#351;i f) constituie motive de revizuire dac&#259; au dus la\npronun&#355;area unei hot&#259;râri nelegale sau netemeinice.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_479249794\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1505\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_479249794\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)În cazul prev&#259;zut la alin. (1) lit. e), toate\nhot&#259;rârile care nu se pot concilia sunt supuse revizuirii.</span></p>"}